text.tspan: Table 10. Vaccine Efficacy Against Centrally Confirmed Moderate to Severe/Critical COVID-19 With
Onset at Least 14 and at Least 28 Days After Vaccination, Per-Protocol Set, Study 3001
Source: Sponsor tables GEFPE02_A and GEFPE02_C
N=Total number of participants at risk per category
